+- `screenshots/after/after-mobile-03-town.png`
+- `screenshots/before/before-desktop-05-run-menu.png`
+- `screenshots/after/after-desktop-05-run-menu.png`
+- `screenshots/after/after-mobile-04-dungeon-hud.png`

